Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:07.11,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:09.57,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In this kingdom where magic is everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:12.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,there is one boy who can't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:18.91,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,With guts and hard work, \Nhe made it into the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:21.70,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and he never gave up, \Ndespite how much he got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:24.70,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He continues to diligently \Naim for the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.79,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are a peasant,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:29.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,or even if you're poor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:32.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone in this world can still shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He's working hard to prove that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:37.87,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and to become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:08.60,Ep Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}To the Heart Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:15.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami! The Heart Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:22.15,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All that's coming through is your \Nenthusiasm. Use your damn words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:25.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gordon's dad looked into it for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:28.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's a stupidly huge \Ncurse in the Heart Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:29.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:32.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can find out something \Nabout the devil's curse
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:34.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,if we go to the Heart Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:37.08,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Gordon? And what \Ndoes he think about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:42.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He was gonna learn some curse magic, \Nso he decided to stay at home for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:48.18,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Also, why did those two come back \Nlooking like their minds are blown?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:51.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Something about the food not \Nagreeing with them or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:54.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I think I got the gist of what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then do I get to go to the Heart Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:00.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make the arrangements, \Nso just sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:08.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.41,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:12.67,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way into the Heart Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:13.96,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:15.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:17.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to go to the Heart Kingdom, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:20.30,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,since the devil's curse is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.07,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The Heart Kingdom has
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:25.10,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,a bunch of its own unique trap \Nspells set up along its border.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.83,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We set any of those off and \Nwe're instant fugitives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:30.10,sign_4918_40_Heart_Kingdom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Heart\NKingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:30.10,sign_4918_41_Clover_Kingdom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Clover Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.10,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Then it'd become an international incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:34.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Oh, but if we nullify the \Ntrap spells with my anti-magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:35.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,we could probably get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:39.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,No, you fool. The moment we mess \Nwith them, they'll find us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.01,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:45.25,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like Rouge isn't going \Nto be able to help either, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.73,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be pretty much impossible \Nto get in without them knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:55.23,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I think Mimosa mentioned \Ngoing to the Heart Kingdom before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She mentioned that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:02.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,there were some nobles going there \Nlike they were exchange students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:06.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Finral. Take these \Njerks to the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.35,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:12.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Finral, you usually complain \Nwhen you get used as an errand boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:16.81,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's someone in the \NGolden Dawn that I want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:19.82,sign_4757_29_Royal_Capital__M,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The Golden Dawn's Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:24.91,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when Finral did his best to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.66,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:33.46,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris! I heard you're awake! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:34.98,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:36.21,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:40.21,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're all right, Miss Finnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.92,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Must be satisfying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:42.72,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:46.74,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to kill my own brother, \Nbut was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:49.73,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when my parents tried \Ndesperately to apologize for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.45,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to kill the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:55.19,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Father must be \Nquite disappointed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.90,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.13,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It all happened because you \Nwere possessed by an elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:00.44,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! We can clear this up—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:04.24,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,On top of everything, I was saved by my\Nbrother, who I've mocked this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:07.28,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:11.89,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You and that peasant are so insolent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.79,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You have no talent, yet you \Ntake on so many burdens!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:18.67,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:24.35,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:27.18,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You being like that makes \Ndeclaring war on you worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.22,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:32.12,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Starting now, I'm going to work hard \Nto make Father acknowledge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a man worthy of being the \Nhead of the House of Vaude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.99,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one who makes Miss Finnes happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:42.60,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to drag you into this, Miss Finnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:43.65,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:47.69,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a man worthy of you, \Nand then I'll come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:53.41,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Please try not to take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:58.91,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:01.63,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Should you be moving, Langris?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.99,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait here, Miss Finnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.17,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:08.99,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm not going to try to gouge \Na bunch of holes in my brother again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:10.67,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty scary, Langris.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.47,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Langris?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:20.00,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,As you are now, you won't be \Nable to make Miss Finnes happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:20.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.56,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:25.08,main,Letoile,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Captain Langris...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:27.38,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So you've awakened as well, Vice Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:30.14,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Look at you cuties!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.87,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,How about we grab some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:35.87,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,See? I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.94,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You're cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:38.74,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:41.15,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You're a hopeless playboy who hits \Non any woman in your path!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:48.01,sign_9601_108_Playboy,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz28\fscx175\pos(146,140)\fscy175\fad(100,1)}Playboy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:42.35,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,P-Playboy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.58,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,All that running away and trying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:44.78,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,to act cool made you a bigger \Nfailure than you already were!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:48.01,sign_9669_112_Failure,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz9\pos(482,61)\fscx175\fscy175}Failure
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:44.78,italicstop,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:48.01,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,And once you pick up bad habits, \Nthey won't be easy to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:48.01,sign_9747_115_Bad_Habits,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-4.89\pos(510,235)}Bad Habits
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:52.19,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,How could someone like you with so \Nmany faults make Miss Finnes happy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.72,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.70,main,Letoile,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are these two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:03.98,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The vice captain has seemed like a \N different person ever since he awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:08.10,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you work hard to \Nrid yourself of that curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:12.49,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I might just end \Nup marrying Miss Finnes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:17.01,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,So was breaking my curse a part \Nof this investigation, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:18.50,sign_4757_29_Royal_Capital__M,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}"No."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:25.49,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. I won't let you be happy \Nthat easily, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:30.22,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So that's why you've come to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.22,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Anything to help Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:37.59,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've been to the Heart Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:40.82,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I went there on an exchange with \Nmy brother when I was thirteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.98,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Though I hated the fact \Nthat it had to be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.87,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,We were only allowed access to a limited area,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.48,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,but their magic techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:52.65,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,are different from the Clover \NKingdom's, so I learned a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:56.02,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lovely kingdom with \Nabundant water and lush greenery,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:59.75,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,and its rich natural environment \Ngenerated so much mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:03.73,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,If what lies at its center \Nis indeed a devil or a curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:05.71,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,that's truly terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.00,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:13.01,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A curse... That might be a clue about \Nthe devil that Mother encountered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:17.09,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't allowed to meet her, but the \Nqueen who rules over the Heart Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:21.02,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,is apparently as powerful as \None of our Magic Knights Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.98,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,She's known as the all-knowing mage who sees
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.15,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,everything that happens in her kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:28.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:33.41,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A queen... Is she like the Witch Queen?\N Then we might be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:36.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess we're not going \Nover there to pick a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:37.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting my guard down, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.13,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I believe they're recruiting applicants \Nto go there right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:43.42,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apply for permission \Nto enter their kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:54.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap! This is the first time \NI've ever been on a ship this huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:57.69,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a cute little ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:09:00.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. We're not going to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you had a boat, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:05.16,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you ever mention it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:09.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I went to go see the mushroom head \Nwho works for Julius and threatened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:11.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,er, discussed the matter with him, \Nand he was happy to lend it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:12.91,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You guys better not damage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:16.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:17.61,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.11,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.34,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're overreacting, Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:25.16,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going over there to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:28.64,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But if something happens while \Nyou're in a different kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:30.92,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,we won't be able to come to your aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.15,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could go with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:37.97,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limit of four... \NSo first, there's Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.47,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The royal lady from the Golden Dawn\N who arranged all of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:45.18,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,And then Noelle, who doesn't seem like \Nshe'll let go of her spot this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.04,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,And lastly, Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:50.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Why am I the fourth one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Having wheels with you comes in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:53.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:54.93,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:57.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Can't really argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.53,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.20,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He is rather convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:03.04,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Spatial magic is convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.64,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:06.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No, really. You don't need to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:10.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! Go kick some ass in the Heart Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.32,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:14.31,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of things there and come home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:16.72,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I still have to fight you, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:17.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:22.34,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If you get homesick and have trouble \Nsleeping, just have a sip of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:23.45,Default,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:24.72,Default,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.21,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That should be enough to send them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:30.48,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you guys didn't forget that \Nyou have a job to do yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.66,Default,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we didn't forget, Mister Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.34,Default,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Off we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.73,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:40.11,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Make sure you all \Nstay on your toes out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:41.43,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:55.35,Default,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Two thousand and thirty-one...\NTwo thousand and thirty-two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:59.01,Default,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Two thousand and thirty-three... \NTwo thousand and thirty-four...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:03.06,Default,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Two thousand and thirty-five... \NTwo thousand and thirty-six...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.01,italicstop,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it steady...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.94,italicstop,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it steady...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:06.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Two thousand and thirty-seven...\NTwo thousand and thirty-eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:06.89,italicstop,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it steady...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:10.42,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Out of all the possibilities, \Nwhy did I have to be stuck on a boat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:13.90,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,with two super-adorable royal cuties \Nand a cool beauty who turns into a bird?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.86,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm gonna be \Nable to sleep at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.62,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Tough it out... Tough it out, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:23.21,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Finnes is the only one for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.20,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.24,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we have some lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:33.25,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you like them, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:36.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you made these, Mimosa? \NI'm digging right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This one's good, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.22,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.14,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Don't eat all of it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:47.74,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This frustrates me for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:49.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I need water!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.38,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:53.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.50,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,For what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:58.90,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I almost fell into the ocean just now, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:12:00.30,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure why, but this frustrates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.82,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that I can't swim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:01.65,top,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:02.93,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.82,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world am I being \Nforced to watch right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.57,top,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How was I supposed to know? I'm royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That doesn't even make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:18.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're actually entering \Nthe Heart Kingdom legally!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We're not coming here to play, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:24.43,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I was only able to \Ngain entry for the four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Mimosa? \NI have nothing but thanks for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:30.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If all else fails, we could \Nuse Finral's spatial magic—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:31.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That would be unlawful entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It got foggy all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:39.69,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who are \Nallowed through this fog
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:43.40,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,are those permitted by the \NQueen of the Heart Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:48.81,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep one bit knowing two \Nbeautiful girls were sleeping near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:52.26,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what does the Queen \Nof the Heart Kingdom look like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.21,italics,Final,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Is she hot, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.58,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Heart Kingdom... I wonder what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:16.10,sign_18968_247_Heart_Kingdom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1004,1)}Heart Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:19.27,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Heart Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:22.28,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Their water sources, the city, and the\N forest are all mixed together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:29.53,main,Loropechika,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they have arrived as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:33.71,main,Loropechika,0000,0000,0000,,The devil power from the Clover Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:36.15,main,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,We must get our hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. I guess this place is sort of pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:45.84,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where we should tie the boat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:50.90,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue sailing forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.10,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.53,top,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Heart Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:58.60,sign_19987_258_Spirit_Guardian_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1005,1)}Spirit Guardian\N{\fs30}Gaja
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:58.60,top,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Spirit Guardian Gaja, \Nand I will act as your guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is he someone important?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.61,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Seems to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:06.75,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,It's been quite some time, Lady Mimosa. \NWe met on your previous visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:08.54,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Good day to you, Gaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:10.87,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored that you remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:15.62,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,You were quite popular with those who \Nhad made your acquaintance, Lady Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:19.63,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This is Asta, Noelle, and Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.13,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.54,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Here is some crimson orange \Njuice that tastes even sweeter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:27.38,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,after some magic is run through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:28.66,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.39,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.33,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this? It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:38.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mine's not sweet at all! Run some\N magic through mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:40.23,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:43.52,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You said to keep sailing, but it \Nlooks like a dead end up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.25,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Fear not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:55.01,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,The queen will transport us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:02.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The queen? So this is just one mage's magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:05.14,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,The mist barrier and the water stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:09.39,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,are a product of the queen's Mana Zone,\N which covers the whole kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:12.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome! And so is this juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:17.26,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He can't be serious. It covers the \Nwhole kingdom? Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:20.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Pretty butterflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.51,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It truly is a lovely kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:26.19,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe there's a devil here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.59,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 1,200 years since \Nour kingdom was founded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.74,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,In every generation, \Nthe queen has made a pact
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.48,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,with the Water Spirit as a priestess,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:36.20,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,and has used its magic to protect the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.69,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Using the power of the water and trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:41.87,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,this has encouraged the development \Nof a magic civilization with deep mana
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.71,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,that does not allow unwanted guests to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:50.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing... A single queen manages \Nto keep peace in a kingdom this big?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.13,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That has been the case up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:57.22,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Though we do not know what the future holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:02.14,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:05.06,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you... What is the \Nmeaning of this, Gaja?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:08.73,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,There's something we need \Nto maintain this peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:11.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to go after Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:14.99,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in our transporter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.02,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.83,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Magic: Fallen Angel's Wingbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:27.25,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... That's only third stage or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.76,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic is rather intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:35.80,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.18,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Lair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:42.76,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:45.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He's floating without using any magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:49.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're trying to do here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:56.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But do you really think you'll \Nget away with harming a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.07,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,of royalty from the Clover Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:01.58,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Noelle! \NShe's super cool, pretty, and cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:04.41,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! Miss Finnes is the only one for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:07.42,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Rare and powerful magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.00,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely first stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.90,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,That's rather impressive water magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:15.76,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,I will not hold back either, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.14,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:32.53,main,Loropechika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for inviting you \Nhere in such a rough manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:38.39,main,Loropechika,0000,0000,0000,,We were waiting for your devil, \Nfor the sake of our kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:42.13,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I just got blown away to some weird place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.91,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Heart Kingdom's queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.50,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.57,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,His attribute is lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:59.80,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Then what were those rune things?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:03.81,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a unique Heart Kingdom \Nmagic technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.61,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Magic: Tenjiolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.19,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:10.44,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But I can evade it with my Valkyrie Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:13.73,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from a first stage. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:19.11,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,I told my spell to pursue \Nyou until it strikes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:32.10,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Gaja, please return Asta to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.63,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, we'll be forced to fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.43,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,An attack spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:39.80,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,It appears Lady Mimosa \Nhas also grown to third stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.49,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like that spatial mage
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:45.13,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,is able to create a path wherever he can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:49.39,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you a glimpse of the \Ndifference between our levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.77,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,He cast his technique into the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.03,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This magic is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:09.83,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are no match for \Nthe vast mana of nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:27.06,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm somehow getting by for now, \Nbut I don't know how much mana they have!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:29.73,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why the heck am\NI even fighting, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:34.18,main,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,So you negate magic... \NThat is your devil's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:34.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:44.46,main,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite abominable, but it\N also seems rather useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:49.31,top,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to meet you, \Ndevil-possessed boy from the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:55.25,sign_28504_355_Water_Spirit_Und,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1004,1)}Water Spirit\N{\fs30}Undine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:53.45,top,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Undine. I'm one of the four \NGreat Spirits, and I'm contracted
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.25,top,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,to the Queen of the Heart Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.34,main,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.34,main,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,but you're no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:06.03,main,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, you don't have \Na lick of magic yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:08.60,main,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,Without any magic, you're less than ninth stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:11.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ninth stage?! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:17.37,main,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. You don't use magic \Nstages in your kingdom, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:22.24,main,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,The lowest is the ninth stage, and then \Nyou have the eighth, the seventh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:26.32,main,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we measure and rank \Nboth magical talent and skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.74,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move... or breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:31.49,main,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,And the highest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.83,main,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,is stage zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:44.76,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,True Lighting Magic: Irial Astrauza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:06.80,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sense their mana \Nanywhere that I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:08.90,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,They must've fled using spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:10.94,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,A wise choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:12.79,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter where they go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.42,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,He accurately manipulated space \Nin a place he couldn't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:20.30,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Plant Creation Magic: Magic Flower Guidepost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:23.31,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Magic: Fallen Angel Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:27.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we can't just back down \Nafter you did all that showing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:31.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:44.07,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but you can't measure our \Ntrue powers by talent alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:46.07,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Magic: Inverse Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:49.82,italics,Undine,0000,0000,0000,,This magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:54.03,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep my anti-magic in reserve\N so she can't pull me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:57.48,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the ki, \Nthere's definitely a person over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:22:00.21,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That means there must be air there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:08.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me! I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.86,0:23:43.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and the others are attacked \Nas they arrive at the Heart Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.35,0:23:47.28,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the Heart Kingdom \Nhas been taken over by a devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:51.20,italics,Some,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i0}Black Clover{\i1}, \NPage 129: "The Devil Megicula."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 129\N\N{\fs18} The Devil Megicula
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:53.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And the queen, Loropechika, appears.
